## Limitations

The analysis is limited by the availability of up-to-date data and the complexity of predicting long-term climate impacts on tourism. Additionally, the regional variability of climate change effects means that findings may not be universally applicable. Further research is needed to explore specific adaptation strategies for different types of tourist destinations.